The best canonical lists on the net

If imitation is the highest form of flattery, then these web pages must represent the highest quality of humor, right? OK, maybe not. But certain types of humor tend to mutate frequently, which causes people to create canonical lists. The following represent some of the best canonical lists available on the Web.
